title.narrative: Natural Resource Management Project

description.narrative: Malawi - Natural Resource Management Project: This project will mitigate the growing problems of aquatic weed infestation and excessive sedimentation in the Shire River Basin to reduce the costly disruptions to Malawi's hydropower generation by investing in weed and sediment management, and implementing better environmental and natural resource management in upstream areas.

title.narrative: Environment and Natural Resources Management
Improving land management for hydropower generation in Malawi
Malawi STAR Report: Full Program Lifecycle Report
Supporting sustainable land management in Malawi

condition.narrative: Further details on conditions precedent affecting this activity can be found in the top-level parent activities.
